### TITLE ###
Float alignment preserves actual precision
### INPUT ###
print("{3.14:>10}")
print("{42.0:<10}")
print("{1.5:>8}")
print("{100.123:<12}")
### STDOUT ###
      3.14
42        
     1.5
100.123     

### TITLE ###
Float alignment with explicit precision
### INPUT ###
print("{3.14:>10.2}")
print("{3.14:>10.4}")
### STDOUT ###
      3.14
    3.1400

